    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Percy writes about the National Book Awards, comments on Hnery James' <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">The golden bowl</title> and Stafford's <title xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:type="simple" render="italic" xlink:href="">A mother in history,</title> compliments a story by
her, and mentions his uncle, a stay at Key West, and current activities and feelings.
</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <arrangement>
      <head>Arrangement
</head>
      <p>The letters are arranged chronologically.
</p>
    </arrangement>
